{\"sentence\": \"Cryptocurrency markets are highly volatile, and investing in digital assets carries significant risk.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No profits are guaranteed, and you may lose some or all of your investment.\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 968, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Always invest responsibly and only with funds you can afford to lose.\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 1038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join OurTelegramchannel to stay up to date on breaking news coverage  The Gods Unchained pricesurgedmore than 24% in the last 24 hours to trade at $0.371 as of 7:35 a.m. EST as investors begin a rapid accumulation of the altcoin.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With this recent gain, the GODS price is in the green by more than 142% on the weekly timeframe.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has also risen over 116% over the past month.\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1416, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"4-hour chart for GODS/USD (Source:GeckoTerminal)  TheGods Unchainedprice is testing the key support level at $0.3480.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5415553475207613e-21, \"text\": \"USD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A 4-hour candle close below this crucial mark within the next 8 hours could expose the crypto to the risk of falling to the subsequent technical safety net at $0.2790.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Conversely, GODS remaining above $0.3480 for the next 12 hours could invalidate the bearish thesis.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In this alternative scenario, the crypto could attempt to flip the $0.4168 resistance level into support.\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thereafter, continued buy pressure might push the altcoin's price to as high as $0.4930 in the following 24 hours.\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Technical indicators on the 4-hour chart for Gods Unchained warn the crypto's price might drop through the course of the next 24 hours.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2074, \"end\": 2088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_collectible_card_game\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gods Unchained\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_collectible_card_game\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_collectible_card_game\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More specifically, the Moving Average Convergence Divergence (MACD) and Relative Strength Index (RSI) indicators are showing bearish signs.\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2305, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The MACD line is currently collapsing towards the MACD Signal line.\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Traders usually see this as a sign of a crypto's bullish momentum losing steam.\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If the gap between the two lines continues to narrow, the MACD line might cross below the MACD Signal line to indicate that GODS has entered a negative short-term trend.\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, RSI readings have been falling over the past 24 hours.\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2637, \"end\": 2640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Repetitive_strain_injury\", \"score\": 0.9290214372993445, \"rank\": 0.07212466129074664, \"text\": \"RSI\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Repetitive_strain_injury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Repetitive_strain_injury\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This could indicate that buyers are losing their strength against sellers.\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Traders will want to keep an eye on this indicator to watch out for a drop below 50.\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Falling below this benchmark might signal a major bearish shift in momentum for the Gods Unchained price.\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While the Gods Unchained price stands the risk of losing the key $0.3480 support, many in thecryptocommunity believe thatThe Meme Games (MGME)tokenmight be the official meme coin for the Paris 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 3171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the Paris 2024 Olympic Games around the corner, crypto investors can get a taste of what it's like to compete at the historic sporting event through The Meme Games (MGME).\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3349, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After purchasing the token during its ongoing ICO, presale participants get to pick between Dogecoin, Pepe, DogWifHat, Brett and Turbo and watch them race for a potential bonus.\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3397, \"end\": 3400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Initial_coin_offering\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7826616917156375e-37, \"text\": \"ICO\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Initial_coin_offering\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Initial_coin_offering\"}, {\"begin\": 3443, \"end\": 3451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dogecoin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dogecoin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dogecoin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dogecoin\"}, {\"begin\": 3453, \"end\": 3457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pepe_the_Frog\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.960627578016512e-15, \"text\": \"Pepe\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pepe_the_Frog\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pepe_the_Frog\"}, {\"begin\": 3480, \"end\": 3485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turbocharger\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.389355495672082e-24, \"text\": \"Turbo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turbocharger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turbocharger\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Should the investor's meme win the race, they will receive a 25% bonus on their purchase amount.\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With just 5 characters to choose from, presale buyers stand a 20% chance to receive the bonus with every purchase.\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3741, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Renowned YouTuber Jacob Crypto Bury predicted in a recent video that the meme coin could soar 100X.\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3774, \"end\": 3778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bury_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999951802303904, \"rank\": 4.8196735757915355e-06, \"text\": \"Bury\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bury_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bury_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The project's presale started with a bang, with investors sending $100k to The Meme Games ICO in a matter of minutes.\", \"from\": 3846, \"to\": 3963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This investor frenzy has continued, as the presale has already raised over $147,000.\", \"from\": 3964, \"to\": 4048, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Apart from the potential to unlock the 25% bonus with every purchase, there is also a lucrative staking opportunity on offer to presale buyers.\", \"from\": 4050, \"to\": 4193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone who acquires and stakes MGME at this early stage gains access to an eye-watering 2,322% APY.\", \"from\": 4194, \"to\": 4293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4289, \"end\": 4292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annual_percentage_yield\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"APY\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annual_percentage_yield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annual_percentage_yield\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To get in on this opportunity, investors can utilize the simple buy widget embedded on the project's website.\", \"from\": 4297, \"to\": 4406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Selling for $0.009, MGME can be bought using either ETH, BNB, USDT or bank card.\", \"from\": 4408, \"to\": 4488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4460, \"end\": 4463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethereum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.485484819356027e-52, \"text\": \"ETH\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethereum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethereum\"}, {\"begin\": 4465, \"end\": 4468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crazy_Arcade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BnB\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crazy_Arcade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crazy_Arcade\"}, {\"begin\": 4470, \"end\": 4474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tether_(cryptocurrency)\", \"score\": 0.982042316310029, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USDT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tether_(cryptocurrency)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tether_(cryptocurrency)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Investors looking to buy the crypto might want to hurry because the crypto's price is scheduled to increase in less than 2 days.\", \"from\": 4489, \"to\": 4617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Purchase and stake MGME here for the 2,322% APY before its price increases.\", \"from\": 4619, \"to\": 4694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4663, \"end\": 4666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.